column5: RHE So the last expiration of the DD date I emailed IR and they responded very quickly stating the buyer had exercised the 3 day extension This time I emailed and all Ive gotten iscrickets On the surface doesnt look good You would think that in the position RHE is in they would have jumped at the chance for some good PR about the contract going binding Time will tell

RHE the day of reckoning of the binary play that is RHE is upon us Two glasses on the right 22 year scotch on the left 1 day old hemlock tea Shall it be champagne wishes and caviar dreams or cardboard boxes and gutter wash Ah yes the old binary playtick tocktick tock
